translated: Bjurulf, Sven Johan, principal, Jönköping, b. 4/1/1891 in Ringamåla, Blekinge. 1st Marriage: Married in 1928 to Stina Lizell. Children: Sven b. 1936, Anna-Stina b. 1941. Education: Studied for a high school diploma in Jönköping in 1909, trained as a primary school teacher in Växjö in 1912, earned a bachelor's degree in 1924. Work: Worked at the Swedish Geological Survey from 1921-1923, 1927-1934, and 1936, taught at Eskilstuna primary school in 1912-1913, Jönköping primary school in 1913-1915, Jönköping high school in 1916-1917, and then became a regular subject teacher in Jönköping and a principal at a practical middle school in 1937.

education.name: Trained as a primary school teacher
